Objects, data storgae, object storage applications

standard tier - objects frequently access, high costs
vault tier - documents only accessed once/twice a month, lower cost
cold vault tier - data needs to be accessed once or twice a year
automatic archiving rules, can take hours, as storage is offline

object storage is low compared to block or file storage

object storage is not good if you need speed

S3 API - OBEJECT STORAGE accessed via API, S3 API - offered by AWS
many object providers offer APIs compatibles with S3 
API - http - restful web services
API call - apps can manage object storage
Object storage can used for new and old apps
Object storage can be used for disaster recovery
